  m_Name: 2 kokonotis
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  planet: 2
  descriptions:
  - Kokonotis is a tropical, watery planet filled with islands and sealife. The planet
    has a mild gravity similar to Earth, as well as very calm winds.
  - The inhabitants - Kokonotians are semi-aquatic creatures with slippery arms and
    hands, which makes them quite unsuited for the game of ArrowHex.
  - However, due to the ideal life conditions, the planet is full of life and, as
    such, has billions of Kokonotians who wish to participate, so despite their challenges,
    they manage to produce players good enough to achieve victory against some planets.
  - "Kokonotis is known as one of the most famous worlds to visit in terms of intergalactic
    tourism, so the intergalactic championship is a great opportunity for Kokonotis
    to showcase it\u2019s various beaches and tropical environments to the world."
